title: PilotsEYE.tv - Quito MD-11F "Lady's Trip to the Closed Stri
description:
Seeing as it was impossible to download this episode of PilotsEYE from the other torrent, I made this from a downloaded BDMV folder and encoded it to MKV.

Unfortunately due to limitations of the Freemake Video Converter, I don't know how to include more than one subtitle in the file, so only English is available.

File is 1080p with the standard German/English audio and English subtitles.

Fellow aviation lovers, enjoy!
